OL,3,CScotland's final group stage match
OL,4,Cagainst Brazil kicks off in Miami
OL,6,FScotland kicked off their final group
OL,7,Fstage match on Wednesday, playing
OL,8,FBrazil at the Miami Stadium.
OL,10,FThe Scottish men's team has never
OL,11,Freached the knockout stages of a major
OL,12,Ftournament, nor have they ever beaten
OL,13,FBrazil in a competitive match.
OL,15,FThey went behind early, with Brazil
OL,16,Fscoring a goal within the first seven
OL,17,Fminutes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
