OL,3,CScotland's final group stage match
OL,4,Cagainst Brazil kicks off in Miami
OL,6,FA win for Scotland against the World
OL,7,FCup giants would secure them an
OL,8,Fautomatic qualification into the
OL,9,Fknockouts.
OL,11,FA draw or narrow defeat would likely
OL,12,Fbe enough to see the team through,
OL,13,Fhowever, a clear defeat would mean a
OL,14,Fwait for Scotland to see if they
OL,15,Fqualify as one of the eight best teams
OL,16,Fin the third ranking.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
