OL,3,CScotland's final group stage match
OL,4,Cagainst Brazil kicks off in Miami
OL,6,FScotland captain Andy Robertson
OL,7,Fadmitted that Brazil will be a tough
OL,8,Fgame, but remained positive, telling
OL,9,Freporters: "We are in control of our
OL,10,Fown destiny."
OL,12,FHis team sits third in Group C after
OL,13,Fopening their campaign with a 1`0 win
OL,14,Fover Haiti, before suffering a 1`0
OL,15,Fdefeat to Morocco.
OL,17,FMorocco's Ismael Saibari scored after
OL,18,Fjust 71 seconds of play against
OL,19,FScotland in Boston on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
