OL,3,CScotland's final group stage match
OL,4,Cagainst Brazil kicks off in Miami
OL,6,FAnticipation has been building in the
OL,7,FFlorida city, where thousands hopeful
OL,8,FScotland of fans have gathered to
OL,9,Fwatch Wednesday's game, with many
OL,10,Fplanning an all-night party should
OL,11,Ftheir team pull off a win.
OL,13,FChris Thomas, aged 42, travelled from
OL,14,FAberdeen to see his team play in the
OL,15,FUS.
OL,17,FHe said it would be a "dream" if
OL,18,FScotland could manage a win against
OL,19,FBrazil, saying: "We'll probably just
OL,20,Fkeep going until the end of the night
OL,21,Fand into the morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
