OL,3,CScotland's final group stage match
OL,4,Cagainst Brazil kicks off in Miami
OL,6,F"Hopefully we can sneak a 2-1 result,
OL,7,Fthat would be good."
OL,9,FITV News Correspondent Peter Smith
OL,10,Freports from Miami ahead of Scotland's
OL,11,FWorld Cup match against Brazil
OL,13,FThe Tartan Army was out in full force
OL,14,Fahead of the match.
OL,16,FFans from both teams were seen
OL,17,Fdrinking, dancing on Ocean Drive, and
OL,18,Fwishing each other luck. Some even
OL,19,Fplayed five-a-sides and other street
OL,20,Ffootball games.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
