OL,3,CScotland's final group stage match
OL,4,Cagainst Brazil kicks off in Miami
OL,6,FThe Scottish fans certainly won over
OL,7,Fthe hearts of people in Boston, where
OL,8,Ftheir previous games were held, as
OL,9,Fthey marched through the city playing
OL,10,Fbagpipes and chanting the new
OL,11,Funofficial "No Scotland, No Party"
OL,12,Fanthem.
